<tr><td><br>

<font FACE="arial, helvetica, geneva" size="-1">


<b>Collecting the Data</b><br>

Political assets generally come from a variety of internal and external sources&#151;human resources, financial services, accounting, PAC information, and so on.  We not only help you determine what data you need, we also help you gather and process it.  The type of data you wish to incorporate into your online system may include the following, as well as other information you need at your fingertips:<br>
<br>
<blockquote>
<li>	Employees;<br>

<li>	Retirees;<br>

<li>	Offices/Facilities;<br>

<li>	Direct economic impact, including aggregate employment and financial information;<br>

<li>	Indirect economic impact, including vendor and supplier relationships and vendor revenue information, as well as major customer relationships;<br>

<li>	Shareholders;<br>

<li>	Corporate or association philanthropy;<br>

<li>	PAC information, including both organization PAC activity and competitor PAC activity. 
</blockquote>

<br>
<b>Synthesizing the Data</b><br>

Democracy Data &amp; Communications cleanses the data and synthesizes it into a unified system that will provide you with comprehensive, detailed political information:
<br>
<br>

<b>Offering Personal Training in the Online System</b><br>

With other systems, you buy a database management program and then get left on your own to figure out how to use it.  That doesn't happen with Democracy Data &amp; Communications.  We know that the most important aspect of your online system will be your familiarity with all its capabilities.  To that end, we provide you with thorough, personalized training and supporting materials that you can refer back to as you need them.  Personal training includes:<br>

<blockquote>
<li>	On-site training of your representatives by Democracy Data &amp; Communications' technical experts;<br>

<li>	Expert installation of the Citrix client software on machines in your offices;<br>

<li>	Manuals and other reference materials.<br>
</blockquote>
<br>


<b>Providing You with Online Access</b><br>

Best of all, online access gives all your representatives the ability to look at the same information instantaneously, whether your offices are down the hall from each other or across the country.
<br>
<br>
<font color="#373096" face="arial" size="+2"><b>Results and Benefits</b></font><br>
<br>

<b>Asset Screens</b><br>

Flexibility and scope are key to the success of your database system.  The Democracy Direct software will convey your data at a variety of levels, so you can view everything from the total picture down to the address and phone number of an individual constituent.  
<br>
<br>

<b>Wizard Screen</b><br>

The wizard screen allows you to run queries and select segments of your data with the ease and convenience of point-and-click technology.
<br>
<br>

<b>Reports and Maps</b><br>

The reports and maps you can produce with the Democracy Direct system will provide you with precisely the information you need for a given issue or project.  From our standard reports to maps and reports customized to your specifications, the database gives you the flexibility to present your data in the most appropriate format.
<br>
<br>

<b>Legislator Profiles</b><br>

The database provides you with up-to-date legislator profiles that can make planning and implementing lobbying and grassroots campaigns a seamless process.
<br>
<br>


<b>Key Contact Information</b><br>

The database puts your key contact and constituent information literally at your fingertips, so you can mobilize grassroots or PAC activity rapidly and document activity as it occurs.
<br>
<br>


<b>Conducting Grassroots Education and Activations</b><br>

The Democracy Direct system offers the perfect means of efficiently educating and mobilizing your strongest political assets&#151;your people.  Between Democracy Data &amp; Communications and our parent company, The Direct Impact Company, we can assist you with:<br>

<blockquote>
<li>	Complete mail-merge, fax broadcast, and email capabilities;<br>

<li>	Compelling, professional direct mail;<br>

<li>	State-of-the-art telephone recruitment;<br>

<li>	Personal, on-the-ground field recruitment.<br>
</blockquote><br>


With the Democracy Direct system, your grassroots and direct lobbying efforts integrate smoothly and work together more effectively.  What's more, your entire government affairs program becomes dramatically more efficient, streamlined, and capable of achieving all your political objectives.



